            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Terentius <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>aviae</ex></expan> Ta&amp;lt;l=I&amp;gt;asiae ob meritis et fide&amp;lt;l=I&amp;gt;itatem <lb n="2"/>totiusque sanctitatem arcam posui coniugi <lb n="3"/>carissimae et sibi quam a parentibus ipsius suscepi <lb n="4"/>annos XVIII quaeque inlibatae mecum vixit annos XXXII <lb n="5"/>tradita sepulturae die Nonarum Septembres <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Valente VI et Va&amp;lt;l=I&amp;gt;entiniano iterum <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cons</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>si quis vero sup&amp;lt;e=I&amp;gt;r duo cor&amp;lt;p=I&amp;gt;ora nos&amp;lt;t=I&amp;gt;ra aliut <note>sic</note> <lb n="8"/>corpus voluerit ordinare dabit fisci viribus <note>sic</note> argenti pondo quindecim 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Deckel verschollen. Z. 9 (Ende): Hedera. (B): Textwiedergabe nach E. Marin u. a.</p>
            </div>
